# CODEOWNERS
# Defines who is automatically requested for review when a PR touches certain paths.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Order matters — the LAST matching rule wins.

# --- Default owner for everything ---
*                                           @Puneethkumarck

# --- CI/CD & GitHub configuration ---
# Any change to workflows, Renovate, or Dependabot config requires owner review
.github/                                    @Puneethkumarck
renovate.json                               @Puneethkumarck

# --- Merchant Onboarding service ---
merchant-onboarding/                        @Puneethkumarck

# --- Merchant IAM service ---
merchant-iam/                               @Puneethkumarck

# --- Infrastructure (Docker Compose, local infra) ---
infra/                                      @Puneethkumarck
docker-compose*.yml                         @Puneethkumarck

# --- Build configuration ---
# Changes to Gradle build files affect the whole project — require careful review
build.gradle.kts                            @Puneethkumarck
settings.gradle.kts                         @Puneethkumarck
gradle.properties                           @Puneethkumarck
gradle/                                     @Puneethkumarck

# --- Security-sensitive files ---
# These files should ALWAYS require owner review, regardless of other rules
SECURITY.md                                 @Puneethkumarck
**/SecurityConfig*                          @Puneethkumarck
**/JwtFilter*                               @Puneethkumarck
**/Auth*                                    @Puneethkumarck
